{
  "texts": [
    "The study concludes that while GPT-4 is better than ChatGPT-3.5, neither AI would likely pass the ABOS written exam [50].",
    "This could be owing to insufficient model training by the engineers and a lack of orthopedic literature utilized in training it.",
    "It could also be due to the complex nature of questions in orthopedic exams.While much attention has been given to ChatGPT, studies have also evaluated other generative AI models like Google Bard (now Gemini) and Bing AI GPT-4.",
    "Vaishya et al.",
    "analyzed the performance of ChatGPT-3.5, ChatGPT-4.0, and Google Bard on 120 postgraduatelevel orthopedic questions [51]."
  ]
}